text: Party is a 2018 Indian Marathi language comedy drama film directed by Sachin Darekar. The film stars Suvrat Joshi,Akshay Tanksale,Prajakta Mali,Stavan Shinde Rohit Haldikar and Manjiri Pupala in the lead roles.
